Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.90,0:00:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躲开 躲开 快跳船
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.66,0:00:51.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下搞不好要完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.37,0:00:54.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 刚才那下我家附近炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.13,0:00:58.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.68,0:01:10.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.97,0:01:12.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.52,0:01:21.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.94,0:01:25.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.53,0:01:29.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯撒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.41,0:01:31.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.62,0:01:32.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.33,0:01:35.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请带来…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.46,0:01:39.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的安宁…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.82,0:02:51.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 骏骏 没事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.30,0:03:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去救大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.61,0:03:34.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骏骏 师傅他们就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.58,0:03:47.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.26,0:03:56.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.26,0:03:58.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.18,0:04:01.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.48,0:04:08.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十年前 巴哈姆特那混蛋出现时
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.61,0:04:10.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.53,0:04:16.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我答应一个女人会保护好她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.87,0:04:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果我放弃了她的生命选择了这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.16,0:04:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜 你会选哪边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,选他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.31,0:04:44.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去快回 妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界会变成啥样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.86,0:04:57.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事你根本不需要考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.12,0:05:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把那混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.41,0:05:08.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狠狠揍一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.61,0:05:44.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我干掉那家伙之后还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.79,0:05:50.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这条命随你们处置
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.21,0:05:57.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陛下 祝你出师大捷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:01.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,口是心非
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:20.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陛下一到多洛莫斯立刻撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.92,0:07:18.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快撑不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.18,0:07:28.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全军集中力量防守
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.85,0:07:30.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要撑住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.72,0:08:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.34,0:08:49.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一刻等好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.14,0:08:59.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.36,0:09:01.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.48,0:09:02.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.82,0:09:06.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你要献上生命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.03,0:09:10.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就陪你一起献上生命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:25.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没必要跟着送死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.63,0:09:27.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会放弃的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.30,0:09:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是我的生命还是你的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.68,0:09:35.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对不会放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.62,0:10:40.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿米拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.37,0:12:02.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死…死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.75,0:12:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.29,0:12:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得救啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.51,0:12:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个怪物真的死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.33,0:12:49.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可是我引以为傲的徒弟哦 妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.09,0:13:16.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈可否安好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.26,0:13:21.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我如今仍在过着王都的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.89,0:13:22.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.22,0:13:25.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.85,0:13:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王都因复兴工程变得非常繁忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.69,0:13:38.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得知你那边没怎么遭受巴哈姆特的危害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.32,0:13:39.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倍感安心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.03,0:13:46.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天 发生了很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.92,0:13:57.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想必我这辈子都不会忘记那天发生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.76,0:14:00.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该不会忘的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.39,0:14:13.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为英雄的国王从那天起便失明了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.77,0:14:15.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过他还在当国王
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.45,0:14:26.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边的 打起精神来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.87,0:14:30.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了 王都的人类跟恶魔之间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.45,0:14:33.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仇恨消失 和好如初…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.37,0:14:36.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.84,0:14:39.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 不像之前 如今已没有奴隶啥的了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.17,0:14:43.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许关系正在逐渐改变
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:48.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贞德离开了王都
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.51,0:14:51.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说现在住在神界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.77,0:14:54.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打算回老家之后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.31,0:14:57.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再让奶奶驮着我去找她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.08,0:15:08.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.25,0:15:13.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恶魔阿萨谢尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.83,0:15:16.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.13,0:15:20.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.30,0:15:29.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴卡斯还是老样子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.60,0:15:34.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我当成家人 温柔地接纳了我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.52,0:15:37.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 小姑娘 欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.65,0:15:40.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.03,0:15:43.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算赖到啥时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.45,0:15:51.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你俩也来帮帮忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.95,0:15:56.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽塔在那天失去了重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.62,0:15:58.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过现在已经完全振作起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.67,0:16:01.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还给我做了美昧的饭菜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.63,0:16:04.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姑娘的话音…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.01,0:16:07.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然无法恢复啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.14,0:16:12.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 想不到代价竟是话音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.06,0:16:17.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是喊你们来帮忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.48,0:16:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.95,0:16:35.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.08,0:16:40.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的好意我心领了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.55,0:16:46.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个真好喝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.84,0:16:49.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不嫌弃的话 我可以教你怎么做哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.05,0:16:50.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.05,0:16:55.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 代替我给那个醉鬼做如何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.69,0:16:58.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.15,0:17:02.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴卡斯喜欢索菲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.36,0:17:07.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索菲大人怎么可能给这种冒牌神做饭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.03,0:17:10.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说谁是冒牌神啊 蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.53,0:17:14.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们别跟着起哄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.62,0:17:19.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋…别笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.92,0:17:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有机会我会向妈妈介绍这些出色的人的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.00,0:17:27.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说你蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.97,0:17:33.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啦 我可没做你那份料理哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.14,0:17:35.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真遗憾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.68,0:17:39.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 我今天不是来喝酒的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.15,0:17:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得是时候出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.82,0:17:52.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.28,0:17:53.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.87,0:17:58.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我原本就不喜欢王都这地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.87,0:18:01.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是回归放浪生活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.93,0:18:13.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是乎 我明天早上就启程
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.39,0:18:17.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保重哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.03,0:18:28.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.49,0:18:31.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想让我给你个拥抱啥的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.70,0:18:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候 见到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.54,0:18:46.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？见谁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.09,0:18:54.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在巴哈姆特的光芒中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.27,0:19:01.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见到女人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.13,0:19:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,她希望你……
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.96,0:19:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,过得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.09,0:19:34.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.81,0:19:43.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风往哪边吹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.49,0:19:56.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来到王都之后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.32,0:20:00.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开心的事 快乐的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.12,0:20:03.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悲伤得让人想哭的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.29,0:20:06.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各种各样的事发生了好多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.29,0:20:09.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.21,0:20:12.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今后还会过得很好的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.39,0:23:08.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴哈姆特根本没死
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.89,0:23:11.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 阿米拉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.31,0:23:17.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法瓦罗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.91,0:23:28.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.63,0:23:40.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就能重逢的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.91,0:24:02.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴哈巴哈巴哈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.75,0:24:04.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢收看
